nodes.text: Star Wars Insider 198 is the 176th issue of the Star Wars Insider magazine, as well as the 106th issue published by Titan Magazines. It was published on November 10, 2020.

THE COUNTDOWN TO INSIDER #200 BEGINS! GREG GRUNBERG - ace Resistance pilot Snap Wexley - opens up about his love for the saga. ELIZABETH GRULLON discusses her experience playing JEDI: FALLEN ORDER's villainous Second Sister. We count down EMPEROR PALPATINE'S top 5 apprentices - Plus, all the latest news from every sector of the Star Wars galaxy!
